OL,3,CStudy reveals long term health impact
OL,4,Cof toxic smoke on Grenfell firefighters
OL,6,FMore than a quarter of firefighters
OL,7,Fexposed to toxic smoke during the
OL,8,FGrenfell Tower fire have been left
OL,9,Fwith long-term health disorders,
OL,10,Faccording to a new study.
OL,12,FResearch from the University of
OL,13,FCentral Lancashire (UCLan) found that
OL,14,Fof 524 firefighters who tackled the
OL,15,Fblaze in 2017, 136 reported life-
OL,16,Fchanging conditions over the first
OL,17,Fthree years.
OL,19,FThese included 11 cases of cancer, 64
OL,20,Frespiratory diseases, 22 neurological
OL,21,Fdisorders and 66 digestive illnesses.
