OL,6,FWhile there is no proven link between
OL,7,Fthese conditions and Grenfell, the
OL,8,Fresearchers say there is a "strong
OL,9,Fcorrelation" between smoke exposure
OL,10,Fand longer-term adverse health
OL,11,Foutcomes.
OL,13,FAmong those surveyed was Jamie
OL,14,FMcDonnell, 54, who has developed
OL,15,Fincurable cancer since risking his
OL,16,Flife fighting the fire.
OL,18,FSpeaking of the experience, he told
OL,19,FGood Morning Britain: "We just had
OL,20,Findustrial dust masks.
