OL,6,F"We went up to level 13, it was still
OL,7,Fsmouldering, we still had pockets of
OL,8,Ffire. But we should have had full PPE
OL,9,Fthat night. Hindsight's a great thing."
OL,11,FThe report co-author, Professor Anna
OL,12,FStec, who specialises in Fire
OL,13,FChemistry and Toxicity, said the
OL,14,Fmajority of the 136 firefighters who
OL,15,Freported health disorders had not worn
OL,16,Frespiratory protection at all times
OL,17,Fwhile tackling the fire.
