OL,6,FProfessor Stec concluded that this was
OL,7,Fdue to the urgency of the disaster and
OL,8,Fresulted in "debilitating" health
OL,9,Feffects.
OL,11,FThe report also offered the following
OL,12,F'learning outcomes' to protect future
OL,13,Fgenerations of firefighters.
OL,15,FThe research was commissioned by the
OL,16,FFire Brigades Union (FBU) - the
OL,17,FGeneral Secretary Matt Wrack said
OL,18,Ffirefighters deserve more.
