OL,6,FHe told Good Morning Britain: "The UK
OL,7,Fis significantly behind other parts of
OL,8,Fthe world in terms of recognising
OL,9,Fhealth risks to firefighters over the
OL,10,Flong term from contaminants, and
OL,11,Fsecondly, in monitoring the health of
OL,12,Ffirefighters."
OL,14,FA London Fire Brigade spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "We welcome insights that can
OL,16,Flead to better protection for
OL,17,Ffirefighters. We supported the
OL,18,Finvolvement of members of London Fire
OL,19,FBrigade in this research, and we will
OL,20,Fcontinue to work closely on this with
OL,21,Fthe FBU.
